description:
Recently sold: $236,700. Open and bright 4-level sits on a flat, fully fenced lot with nothing behind you but prairie and space. Home boasts large sun filled rooms with a layout that suits nearly every living situation. 

This one sparkles with fresh paint, new carpet and loads of just hard work & sprucing up!!! 4 levels creates wonderful space/separation without the chopped up feel you get in most multi-levels.  Huge entry/foyer, oversized kitchen, owners' suite with walk-in closet, and just so much more.....

Three gathering spaces, spacious & updated kitchen has loads of counter/cupboard space and stainless steel appliances. 

Sellers have done so much recently with fresh paint, new carpet & just a lot of hard work.  Come see & bring your ideas along to finish what they have started.....
3rd BR still needs to be finished along with closet and 1/4 bath to make it full.
4th BR listed is currently an amusement/TV room.

Still work to do here that will create instant equity and more finished space to use. Sheetrock, carpet, and paint needed in most of 3rd level. Sellers will leave vanity they purchased so finishing that bath is just a touch easier. They thought about finishing but decided best for them and your client to just leave as is, reflect that in the price, and let new owners do what, when, and how they want!!!

So close to schools, shopping, and dining and yet so much nature in your very own back yard.
